I hope you can stop ordering takeout.

256
00:17:55,478 --> 00:17:57,197
Don't just drink yogurt and eat salads

257
00:17:57,197 --> 00:18:00,438
just because you're in a hurry to lose weight.

258
00:18:00,438 --> 00:18:02,977
Actually, the kitchen is not as scary as you think.

259
00:18:02,977 --> 00:18:04,817
Every now and then, you can come to the kitchen

260
00:18:04,817 --> 00:18:07,198
and prepare your own favorite dishes.

261
00:18:07,198 --> 00:18:08,938
When your stomach feels warm,

262
00:18:08,938 --> 00:18:11,158
so will your life.

263
00:18:17,818 --> 00:18:20,117
It's done. What's next?

264
00:18:20,117 --> 00:18:21,998
Here.

265
00:18:21,998 --> 00:18:23,858
Watch me.

266
00:18:35,708 --> 00:18:38,778
Start by coring the pears.

267
00:18:43,570 --> 00:18:45,920
Open up.

268
00:18:52,778 --> 00:18:58,408
Then, put the pear cubes and the white fungus that we soaked in water into the saucepan.

269
00:18:58,408 --> 00:19:01,597
Don't forget, Add two preserved plums.

270
00:19:04,018 --> 00:19:06,838
Then, simmer for two hours, and it's ready.

271
00:19:06,838 --> 00:19:08,318
Okay, it's done.

272
00:19:09,538 --> 00:19:12,197
Mr. Song's class is over. See you tomorrow.

273
00:19:12,197 --> 00:19:13,958
- Bye.
- Bye.

274
00:19:15,198 --> 00:19:18,017
- Come on.
- Bye.
- Let's arrange the photos.

275
00:19:53,738 --> 00:19:55,598
I have something to tell you.

276
00:19:55,598 --> 00:19:56,817
After I'm done packing up.

277
00:19:56,817 --> 00:19:58,518
No need for that.

278
00:20:00,100 --> 00:20:02,000
You don't have to come with me.

279
00:20:03,200 --> 00:20:04,900
Don't worry about Huateng.

280
00:20:04,900 --> 00:20:07,600
Although my dad has stepped back and handed over the reins,

281
00:20:07,600 --> 00:20:10,700
he'll still help to keep an eye on things.

282
00:20:10,700 --> 00:20:13,900
Also, I'm thinking about hiring a professional manager.

283
00:20:13,900 --> 00:20:15,600
That way, even if I'm not around,

284
00:20:15,600 --> 00:20:17,800
the company can still operate as usual.

285
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:35,800
It's not Huateng that I'm worried about.

286
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:39,200
I'm worried about you.

287
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:41,000
Qingchun.

288
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:44,400
I don't want you to hit pause because of me,

289
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:48,000
nor do I want you to be trapped inside the ward

290
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:52,600
and waiting every day for something that might never happen.

291
00:20:53,800 --> 00:20:55,000
I'm not afraid.

292
00:20:55,000 --> 00:20:57,200
But it pains me if that happens.

293
00:20:58,000 --> 00:20:59,600
Let me ask you this.

294
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,800
Do you still remember your dreams?

295
00:21:03,900 --> 00:21:05,800
None of those matters.

296
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:07,400
No.

297
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:09,700
Those things matter to me.

298
00:21:11,100 --> 00:21:13,000
I always remember

299
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:15,700
your confidence and charm in front of the cameras,

300
00:21:16,400 --> 00:21:19,000
and the sparkle in your eyes

301
00:21:19,000 --> 00:21:21,800
when you talked about the design of future programs

302
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:24,100
and your dream of becoming a producer

303
00:21:24,100 --> 00:21:26,000
during the interview.

304
00:21:28,400 --> 00:21:30,800
You gave up all those because of Huateng.

305
00:21:31,900 --> 00:21:36,000
Right now, could you start all over for me?

306
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:44,900
I gave you my word

307
00:21:45,500 --> 00:21:47,600
that I would fight to live

308
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:50,000
and you wouldn't suffer.

309
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:52,500
But I hope you can promise me one thing.

310
00:21:53,800 --> 00:21:56,000
When I see you again,

311
00:21:57,200 --> 00:21:58,600
let me see that you have lived

312
00:21:58,600 --> 00:22:01,400
the life that you always wanted.

313
00:22:01,400 --> 00:22:03,600
Don't make me feel

314
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:05,700
like I'm a burden to you.

315
00:22:09,400 --> 00:22:10,700
Okay.

316
00:22:12,400 --> 00:22:13,700
I promise.

317
00:22:17,200 --> 00:22:19,200
I'll wait for you at home.

318
00:22:40,270 --> 00:22:41,910
[MIA]

