321
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:51,000
It's beautiful.

322
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:53,200
That too! That one.

323
00:22:54,700 --> 00:22:57,000
This is my favorite tutu skirt.

324
00:22:57,600 --> 00:22:59,200
Look at this.

325
00:23:00,800 --> 00:23:03,000
Blue and pink have always been the perfect pair.

326
00:23:03,000 --> 00:23:05,100
I'm sure Director Su will be so surprised

327
00:23:05,100 --> 00:23:07,400
