329
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:10,200
Me.

330
00:23:10,200 --> 00:23:12,400
You called to make a reservation yesterday, right?

331
00:23:12,400 --> 00:23:13,400
Please come with me.

332
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:14,800
Let's go.

333
00:23:30,300 --> 00:23:32,300
