00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,800
Okay.

345
00:24:06,800 --> 00:24:08,800
Excuse me.

346
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,700
I'll try this.

347
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,600
Cong Cong.

348
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:23,800
You're so beautiful.

349
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,600
Not bad.

350
00:24:30,700 --> 00:24:31,800
Sir.

351
00:24:31,800 --> 00:24:35,100
This suit comes together with the wedding dress.

352
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:39,800
That's perfect.

353
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:41,800
I'll take the wedding dress too.

354
00:24:41,800 --> 00:24:43,000
I'll take this.

