00:33:02,200 --> 00:33:04,400
Come on. I'll take you to a place.

481
00:33:04,400 --> 00:33:06,400
I want to take you somewhere too.

482
00:33:06,400 --> 00:33:10,500
Well, let's see if we're going to the same place.

483
00:33:11,900 --> 00:33:13,600
Let's go.

484
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:23,200
Where are you taking me to?

485
00:33:23,200 --> 00:33:25,400
Have a guess.

486
00:33:25,400 --> 00:33:27,300
What are you up to again?

487
00:34:04,100 --> 00:34:06,400
- Why are you here?
- Why are you here?

488
00:34:07,800 --> 00:34:09,900
Are you helping Director Su with the wedding preparation?

489
00:34:09,900 --> 00:34:12,800
So you reserved the wedding dress for Song Qingchun?

490
00:34:12,800 --> 00:34:15,000
What do you think then?

491
00:34:15,000 --> 00:34:17,600
Are you expecting something else?

492
00:34:19,000 --> 00:34:22,000
Don't tell Director Su about it. We'll do our own thing.

493
00:34:40,700 --> 00:34:43,100
The wedding officially begins!

494
00:34:43,100 --> 00:34:46,100
Let's have the two most important men in the bride's life

495
00:34:46,100 --> 00:34:48,400
perform the sacred ceremony of giving away the bride.

496
00:34:48,400 --> 00:34:50,600
Let's have the bride enter the hall.

497
00:36:07,900 --> 00:36:09,700
Qingchun.

498
00:36:11,100 --> 00:36:12,700
Zhinian.

499
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:16,000
When two people are together,

500
00:36:16,000 --> 00:36:18,600
it's not one plus one equals two.

501
00:36:18,600 --> 00:36:22,400
But two halves form one

502
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:24,800
to become each other's other half

503
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:27,600
and form a perfect family.

504
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:32,000
I believe you'll treat my daughter well.

505
00:36:33,600 --> 00:36:35,100
Zhinian.

506
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:41,000
I'll hand over my daughter to you today.

507
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:43,600
From today onward,

508
00:36:43,600 --> 00:36:47,800
I'm not only Qingchun's dad,

509
00:36:47,800 --> 00:36:50,200
but I'm also your dad.

510
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:55,600
We'll wait for you to come home.

511
00:36:56,800 --> 00:36:59,600
Thank you, Dad.

512
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:15,200
I have a few words to say before the bride and groom exchange vows.

513
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,800
Frankly speaking,

514
00:37:21,800 --> 00:37:25,200
I never thought I would be hosting Su Zhinian's wedding.

515
00:37:25,200 --> 00:37:28,200
After all, for a period of time in the past,

516
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:31,600
he used to be a rational cold-blooded creature.

517
00:37:31,600 --> 00:37:33,400
Besides me,

518
00:37:33,400 --> 00:37:36,400
no one can stand his bad temper.

519
00:37:39,300 --> 00:37:41,000
I once thought

520
00:37:41,000 --> 00:37:45,100
that we would live in a nursing home when we grew old.

521
00:37:45,100 --> 00:37:48,000
I'd stand out against him

522
00:37:48,000 --> 00:37:50,600
and be the most popular old man.

523
00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:53,600
But now,

524
00:37:53,600 --> 00:37:56,600
as you can see, this plan fell through.

525
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:58,800
At first,

526
00:37:58,800 --> 00:38:01,600
I was against Mr. Su's choice.

527
00:38:01,600 --> 00:38:05,600
But now, I'm thankful to Miss Song

528
00:38:05,600 --> 00:38:10,100
